62  def _callback_set_digital_io(self, req):
63  if req.name in self._digital_outputs:
64  self._digital_outputs[req.name].value = req.value
65  elif req.name in self._digital_inputs:
66  self._digital_inputs[req.name].value = req.value
67  elif req.name in self._analog_inputs or req.name in self._analog_outputs:
68  return self._create_response(CommandStatus.DIGITAL_IO_PANEL_ERROR,
69  "{} is not a digital io.".format(req.name))
70  else:
71  # No pin found
72  return self._create_response(CommandStatus.DIGITAL_IO_PANEL_ERROR, "No IO found for {}".format(req.name))
73  self._publish_digital_io_state()
74  return self._create_response(CommandStatus.SUCCESS, "Successfully set value for {}".format(req.name))
